tion mismatch."],"human_review_triggers":["If the intended product behavior is that only the post-save note editor and links page auto-refresh, the reliability wording should be narrowed explicitly rather than left broad.","If the intended behavior is truly 'pending owner views' across the knowledge-studio UI, additional UI polling/refresh coverage is still needed on dashboard/search/tags before promotion."]}
